data.description: Super cute lake house with wide open water view. Open living area with wall of windows,  WBFP, tons of light, eating bar. Kitchen has newish appliances and lots of counter space and storage. Master on water side with access to covered porch. Large secondary bedroom with access door to exterior. 3rd bedroom nestled between the 2 bathrooms. Located in gated community, perfect orientation on the water. Boathouse has boat slip with lift and a fishing or swimming deck. Steel retaining wall with concrete sidewalk. Plush, established lawn, mature trees. Wonderful porch on lakeside for extended outdoor living area. Perfect for lake watching!! Includes a lot across the street with matching storage building. Septic runs to the lot across the street. Cute and clean home, needs a small bit of foundation work on the bedroom side around the area of the conversion and priced accordingly. Quote for repair in documents. Sold As-Is!
